{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "auth-service-complete",
    "name": "AuthService API - Complete Test Suite",
    "description": "Central Kitchen Franchise System - AuthService Complete API Testing Collection\n\n**Features:**\n- Automated token management\n- Role-based user testing (5 roles)\n- JWT validation tests\n- Token blacklisting verification\n- User sync endpoint testing\n\n**⚠️ IMPORTANT - How to Run:**\n1. Import this collection into Postman\n2. Base URL is set to: http://localhost:8080 ✅\n3. **RUN FOLDERS IN THIS ORDER:**\n   - Step 1: 🔐 Authentication & Authorization (Login first!)\n   - Step 2: 👥 User Synchronization (uses token from Login)\n   - Step 3: 🚪 Logout & Token Revocation\n   - Step 4: 🧪 JWT Token & Claims Validation\n   - Step 5: 📊 Test Scenarios & Workflows\n4. Tokens will auto-save to {{jwt_token}}, {{admin_token}}, etc.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
